In AB, gender is significant (unlike in BC), but not in combination with umultiling.
While we can rely on women showing higher slai regardless of what else is in the analysis, the direction and significance of the umultiling effect in interaction seems to be unreliable/subject to chance.

Given the insignificance of umultiling we focus instead on edu.
